== History ==
'''Heavy Botlane''' was formed by [[Nardeus]], [[Hiiva]] and brothers [[Cabochard]] and [[Istari]] to compete for a spot in the [[2014 EU Challenger Series/Spring Series|EU Coke Challenger Series]]. After finishing off the roster by picking up jungler [[Airwaks]], the team faced off against [[Cloud 9 Europe]], unfortunately falling to them. The team's goal is prepare for the next Play In to win a spot in the Coke League.

